### Variables
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/music
@albumId = 1
@artistId = 1
@start = 2025-01-01T00:00:00Z
@end = 2025-11-01T23:59:59Z
@prevStart = 2024-11-01T00:00:00Z
@prevEnd = 2024-12-01T23:59:59Z

### Resumo semanal
GET {{baseUrl}}/summary?range=week
Accept: application/json

### Resumo mensal
GET {{baseUrl}}/summary?range=month
Accept: application/json

### Resumo personalizado
GET {{baseUrl}}/summary?range=custom&start={{start}}&end={{end}}
Accept: application/json

### Stats globais
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats
Accept: application/json

### Recorte anual
GET {{baseUrl}}/year/2025?limitAlbums=80&limitArtists=12&limitTracks=12
Accept: application/json

### Últimos álbuns ouvidos
GET {{baseUrl}}/recent-albums?limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Biblioteca de artistas
GET {{baseUrl}}/library/artists?limit=24
Accept: application/json

### Biblioteca de álbuns
GET {{baseUrl}}/library/albums?limit=24
Accept: application/json

### Biblioteca de faixas
GET {{baseUrl}}/library/tracks?limit=24
Accept: application/json

### Top artistas do período
GET {{baseUrl}}/tops/artists?start={{start}}&end={{end}}&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Top álbuns do período
GET {{baseUrl}}/tops/albums?start={{start}}&end={{end}}&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Top faixas do período
GET {{baseUrl}}/tops/tracks?start={{start}}&end={{end}}&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Top gêneros do período
GET {{baseUrl}}/tops/genres?start={{start}}&end={{end}}&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Página do álbum (detalhes + faixas)
GET {{baseUrl}}/albums/{{albumId}}
Accept: application/json

### Página do artista
GET {{baseUrl}}/artists/{{artistId}}
Accept: application/json

### Página da faixa
GET {{baseUrl}}/tracks/1
Accept: application/json

### Busca geral (nome de artista, álbum ou música)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=therion&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Busca álbuns nunca ouvidos, limit default=50
GET {{baseUrl}}/albums/never-played?limit=50
Accept: application/json

### Busca o quanto já ouviu dos albums
GET {{baseUrl}}/coverage/albums?limit=50
Accept: application/json

### Busca o quanto já ouviu dos artitas
GET {{baseUrl}}/coverage/artists?limit=50
Accept: application/json


### Trending gêneros (período atual vs anterior)
GET {{baseUrl}}/genres/trending?start={{start}}&end={{end}}&compareStart={{prevStart}}&compareEnd={{prevEnd}}&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Gêneros recentes (últimos N plays)
GET {{baseUrl}}/genres/recent?limit=50
Accept: application/json

### Underplayed gêneros (pouco tocados, mas presentes na biblioteca)
GET {{baseUrl}}/genres/underplayed?start={{start}}&end={{end}}&minLibraryAlbums=3&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Top gêneros por fonte (PLEX vs MUSICBRAINZ vs LASTFM)
GET {{baseUrl}}/genres/top-by-source?start={{start}}&end={{end}}&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Revisão de duplicatas de faixa
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/track-duplicates?limit=20&includeIgnored=false
Accept: application/json

### Marcar grupo como ignorado
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/track-duplicates/ignore
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "albumId": 1,
  "groupKey": "example-group",
  "ignored": true
}

### Mesclar um grupo
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/track-duplicates/merge
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "albumId": 1,
  "groupKey": "example-group",
  "targetTrackId": 10,
  "sourceTrackIds": [11, 12]
}

### Mesclar grupos em lote
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/track-duplicates/merge-batch
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "merges": [
    {
      "albumId": 1,
      "groupKey": "example-group",
      "targetTrackId": 10,
      "sourceTrackIds": [11, 12]
    }
  ]
}
